<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Merciful Broken Sun"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Adam Gubman"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Monster Siren Records"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Rachael Gillespie"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="塞壬唱片-MSR"/><amll:meta key="album" value="慈悲灯塔 (Original Soundtrack)"/><amll:meta key="album" value="慈悲灯塔OST"/><amll:meta key="album" value="慈悲燈塔OST"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="TWU712401524"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2151083894"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000JTfnh4QkcTm"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="486870752"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="74W5hk3S7Hc2KM5U5ZgYYO"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1744942118"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="1:38.960"><div begin="1:09.950" end="1:38.960"><p begin="1:09.950" end="1:12.350" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.950" end="1:10.550">Bro</span><span begin="1:10.550" end="1:11.160">ken</span> <span begin="1:11.160" end="1:12.350">sun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">破碎的太阳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">破碎的太陽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">砕けた太陽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부서진 태양</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Soleil brisé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sol roto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerbrochene Sonne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sol despedaçado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Разбитое солнце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sole infranto</span></p><p begin="1:13.440" end="1:17.390" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.440" end="1:13.670">Sh</span><span begin="1:13.670" end="1:13.860">ed</span><span begin="1:13.860" end="1:14.080">ding</span> <span begin="1:14.080" end="1:14.470">ligh</span><span begin="1:14.470" end="1:14.530">t</span> <span begin="1:14.530" end="1:14.910">on</span> <span begin="1:14.910" end="1:15.340">e</span><span begin="1:15.340" end="1:15.440">ve</span><span begin="1:15.440" end="1:16.060">ry</span><span begin="1:16.060" end="1:17.390">one</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将光芒照拂每一个生灵</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將光芒照拂每一個生靈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">全ての人を照らし出す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">모든 이를 비춰주네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Éclairant tout le monde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Derramando luz sobre todos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Licht auf alle wirft</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Derramando luz sobre todos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Проливающее свет на всех</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Spargendo luce su tutti</span></p><p begin="1:19.670" end="1:22.200" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.670" end="1:20.270">Bro</span><span begin="1:20.270" end="1:20.870">ken</span> <span begin="1:20.870" end="1:22.200">sun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">破碎的太阳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">破碎的太陽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">砕けた太陽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부서진 태양</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Soleil brisé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sol roto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Zerbrochene Sonne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sol despedaçado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Разбитое солнце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sole infranto</span></p><p begin="1:23.300" end="1:27.200" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.300" end="1:23.560">You</span> <span begin="1:23.560" end="1:23.770">are</span> <span begin="1:23.770" end="1:24.170">not</span> <span begin="1:24.170" end="1:24.610">the</span> <span begin="1:24.610" end="1:25.120">on</span><span begin="1:25.120" end="1:25.730">ly</span> <span begin="1:25.730" end="1:27.200">one</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你并不是孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你並不是孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あなたは一人ではない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너만 홀로 남겨진 게 아니야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu n&apos;es pas la seule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No eres la única</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du bist nicht die Einzige</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você não é a única</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты не одиноко</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non sei il solo</span></p><p begin="1:29.720" end="1:34.120" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.720" end="1:30.200">Whoa-</span><span begin="1:30.200" end="1:30.430">oh-</span><span begin="1:30.430" end="1:30.950">oh</span> <span begin="1:30.950" end="1:31.250">they</span> <span begin="1:31.340" end="1:31.750">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:31.750" end="1:32.120">take</span> <span begin="1:32.260" end="1:32.850">my</span> <span begin="1:32.850" end="1:33.030">s</span><span begin="1:33.030" end="1:34.090">par</span><span begin="1:34.090" end="1:34.120">k</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">喔 他们无法夺走我的星火</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">喔 他們無法奪走我的星火</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ 私の灯火は誰にも奪えはしない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">워어어, 그 누구도 내 불꽃을 빼앗을 순 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Oh-oh-oh ils ne peuvent me prendre mon étincelle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Whoa-oh-oh no pueden quitarme mi chispa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Whoa-oh-oh sie können mir meinen Funken nicht rauben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Whoa-oh-oh eles não podem levar a minha centelha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Во-о-о им не отнять мою искру</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Whoa-oh-oh non possono portarmi via la scintilla</span></p><p begin="1:34.570" end="1:38.960" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.570" end="1:34.930">I</span> <span begin="1:34.930" end="1:35.390">won&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:35.390" end="1:35.780">le</span><span begin="1:35.780" end="1:35.860">t</span> <span begin="1:35.860" end="1:36.220">you</span> <span begin="1:36.220" end="1:36.620">go</span> <span begin="1:36.620" end="1:38.960">dark</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我也绝不会让你坠入黑暗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我也絕不會讓你墜入黑暗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あなたを暗闇に沈ませはしない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 빛이 꺼지게 두지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne te laisserai pas t&apos;éteindre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No dejaré que te apagues</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich lasse dich nicht erlöschen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não deixarei você se apagar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не позволю тебе угаснуть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ti lascerò spegnere</span></p></div></body></tt>